      "content": "that sounds really scary... i didn't realize it was that serious. i don't really want to go to the hospital if i don't have to, it's so expensive and the wait times are terrible. is there anything else i can take instead that's safe? maybe something like acetaminophen or tylenol? is that okay to take with warfarin?",
